{"tid":1510830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說「送頭」，試著說「放手一搏」","createTime":"2019-08-27T10:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T15:46:52.000Z","uid":33307,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"442b2e7885a691a72d71aa091934e6d8e4a118fa","tid":1510830,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:27:01.000Z","msg":"睇返民陣係點講冷氣軍事口中既「送頭」（7月2日）<br />\n<br />\n民陣透過社交媒體發家書，指理解及明白抗爭者選擇，「昨夜一眾學子，奮不顧身，放手一搏，其實只是踏出了比我們所有人都更有勇氣的一步」，批評政府經歷多次大遊行、3人自殺身亡後仍不為所動，籲不同想法的港人站在雞蛋的一方，不指摘、不割席。"},{"pid":"ae23f105a88457787b5b3a5e81fd364298411732","tid":1510830,"uid":295904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:28:03.000Z","msg":"岩聽！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奮不顧身<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915a9e82e8461b186aeca7d2c6e078b2ff6966e6","tid":1510830,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:28:34.000Z","msg":"whatever it takes"},{"pid":"96120f72afe2042e8451fd12f684749458e6fa78","tid":1510830,"uid":33307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ae23f105a88457787b5b3a5e81fd364298411732","tid":1510830,"uid":295904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:28:03.000Z","msg":"岩聽！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奮不顧身<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:30:56.000Z","msg":"「放手一搏」/「奮不顧身」✅<br />\n「送頭」❌"},{"pid":"ad32f5558019751069147733b1e537b5d372f069","tid":1510830,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"915a9e82e8461b186aeca7d2c6e078b2ff6966e6","tid":1510830,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:28:34.000Z","msg":"whatever it takes"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:35:06.000Z","msg":"I go to school by bus"},{"pid":"859ae8221a87742363734ee98a1ecbab4a18e120","tid":1510830,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"